# [Slow launch for some GTK apps](https://github.com/swaywm/sway/issues/5732)
exec dbus-update-activation-environment --systemd DISPLAY WAYLAND_DISPLAY SWAYSOCK

# Fix JetBrain IDE's showing properly
exec wmname LG3D

